``pixel_color.py`` provides an example of using PIL/pillow
instead of ImageMagick (``convert``) to take the mean of an image.

``cli.py`` is an example of the use of ``argparse``. ::

    usage: Map polygon and feature extractor [-h] [--without-opencv]
                                             [--keep-temporary-files]
    
    optional arguments:
      -h, --help            show this help message and exit
      --without-opencv
      --keep-temporary-files, -k
